Ed Sheeran’s Carpool Karaoke Features One Very Silly Justin Bieber Story

Sign us up to drive the next time Ed Sheeran needs a ride. The singer finally joined James Corden for a little Carpool Karaoke tonight, and it had pretty much everything any Ed Sheeran…
